SUMMARY:Nashville Meets the Symphony
DESCRIPTION:A Heartland Hit Parade!\nGet ready for a night where the soul of country collides with the power of the orchestra in a show-stopping celebration of America’s music. From twang to triumph\, heartbreak to high notes\, this Heartland concert brings the raw emotion of classic and modern country to life like never before. \nFeel the thrill as the Roanoke Symphony Orchestra takes on unforgettable hits from Miranda Lambert\, Carrie Underwood\,\nZac Brown Band\, Vince Gill\, Tim McGraw\, Dolly Parton\, The Chicks\, Johnny Cash\, and more! \nOne stage. One night. All heart.\nDon’t miss this electrifying tribute to country’s greatest legends! \nThank you to our Sponsors!
URL:https://rso.com/event/nashville-meets-the-symphony/
LOCATION:Salem Civic Center\, 1001 Roanoke Blvd\, Salem\, VA\, 24153\, United States
CATEGORIES:Pops
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://rso.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/seasons-art-elements9.jpg
